race.comment: This is a race of forgiveness. BLUE SPECIAL (1) was good two back at the provincials when runner-up, then better than it looked last time at Gawler when he came from last to finish midfield. Won only try this course and distance and worth another chance. STRAZZ (6) is struggling to find best last few but is back in grade and back at home. Did win only try course and distance and with a nice alley can improve out of sight. WHISKEY 'N' WOMEN (4) is another who was well off best last time but that was in richer company. The start prior was having first try here at this trip and after getting back stormed home into third. Can feature here with a repeat of that run. SHARMA PRINCESS (11) is resuming and while yet to win fresh does kick off at home and is fitter for two jump-outs. Placed only try course and distance. SEE DE NIGHT (7) is fitter for two runs back and looks ready to win after finishing runner-up latest.
